⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Maharito
node MSC · MSC · ⟦Maharito:MSC:632b43⟧

WHO   — Maharito — the warlord of Castle Garland
WHAT  — The antagonist of Milon's Secret Castle — the warlord who took the castle by dark power and holds Queen Eliza captive, the final enemy a boy with bubbles must overcome to win the kingdom back.
WHERE — MSC · Milon's Secret Castle  Framework inputs: Milon's Secret Castle (Hudson Soft, NES 1988)  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because power taken is a castle held; because a throne seized must be guarded to the last room; because every climber who comes for the queen must first be turned away by the one who waits at the top.
HOW   — By sorcery and dominion — the dark power that took the castle and keeps it, the guarded depths and the final stand that the hero must break through.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  The castle is mine, the queen is mine, and the top of this tower is the last thing any small brave boy will ever see.

